value.0: These are the current gameplay changes, all classes welcome.
TTS= See Invis + Ultravision. If you have 70 Spot or 80 Listen (subject to change), then you get True Truesight per spell decription.
- Use Magical Device (UMD) is accurate to the Dungeon Masters guide. There is a higher chance of failure. Random effects happen to caster upon failure, including death.

-Pick Pocket DC is 2.5 * target level.
* A level 30 target would have a DC 75.
* A level 40 target would have DC 100.
* A level 15 target would have DC 38
-AB/AC is capped at +5 on gear. Some unique items may have slightly higher stats.

Support for an unarmed Shifter:
If the shifter has both hands empty and is wearing gloves that 
have damage on them, when the shifter changes into a form the
form will be unarmed, and the gloves properties will be copied
to the forms claws, bite, gore, and/or slam respectively.
This is intended for, but not limited to builds that incorperate
a monk in them.

The script for the shifter has been updated to accomidate three 
major stackable properties: AC, Attributes, and Regeneration.
The script will copy weapon properties only to forms using weapons,
the unarmed handling is detailed above.

Additional Shapes as Follows:
Greater Wildshape 2: Ogre, Gorgon
Greater Wildshape 3: Will'O'Wisp, Umber Hulk
Greater Wildshape 4: Frost Giant, Grey Render
Humanoid Shape     : Gnoll, Stinger
Undead Shape       : Bodak, Mummy Lord
Outsider Shape     : Formian Myrmarch, Hound Archon
Construct Shape    : Battle Horror, Mithral Golem
Dragon Shape       : Ancient Shadow Dragon, Prismatic Dragon
